---
layout: base.njk
title: Insights
description: Perspectives on digital strategy, transformation, and delivery in the built environment.
---

<header class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Insights</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Perspectives on digital strategy and delivery</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="insights-list">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    {% set insightPosts = collections.insights %}
    {% if insightPosts.length > 0 %}
      {% for post in insightPosts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="insight-preview">
        <div class="insight-preview-meta">
          {% if post.data.category %}<span>{{ post.data.category }}</span>{% endif %}
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateISO }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
        </div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.excerpt or post.content | excerpt }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <p>Insights coming soon. We're preparing perspectives on digital strategy, transformation, and delivery in the built environment.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
